evam ity uktakramadiśā svaparahitaprayojanam avagamya pratipattisāro bhavet.

<commentary>idānīṃ saṃprajanyakāritāṃ śikṣayitum āha.

caturṇām īryāpathānām anyatamasminn īryāpathe. kāyenaivam iti sthitena niṣaṇṇena vā avastheyam iti. tadanantaraṃ svādhyāyādikriyām ārabhya punar antarāle vyavalokitavyaṃ kathaṃ kāyaḥ sthita iti tasminn everyāpathe, uta bhinne īryāpathe. bhinne punaḥ pūrvavad avasthāpyaḥ.</commentary>

kāyapratyavekṣām abhidhāya cittapratyavekṣaṇām āha. dharmasya svaparahitalakṣaṇasya cintaiva mahāstambhaḥ, vandhanāyattīkaraṇahetutvāt.
